name: Usagi Tsukino (fanart) - Sailor Moon
description:
For gentle people of culture only! This was trained almost exclusively on NSFW material.

Here it is finally. I had my doubts on making it correctly. If by any chance you want some lolishit then begone, this was trained mostly on Kuroinu Juu and glamourworks.

There are several good enough Sailor Moon Loras which is why I kept postponing this, also the NAI model family do a good job by themselves in a pinch. But I wanted my own SM Lora with Black jack and hookers!

I managed to more or less isolate the following outfits

  • SMEternalOutfit (yellow and black skirt might require puffy_sleeves as the Kuroinu variant often is sleeveless )

  • SMStandardOutfit(Normal outfit, for some reason has the highest variability despite the largely homogeneous dataset. so it might need some retries.)

  • SMPrincessOutfit (came out nicely it is her white and gold dress. )

  • SMSuperOutfit (somewhat iffy white blue and yellow skirt has some bleedover but works fine enough)

  • SMSchoolUniform (Normal school uniform which resembles her standard outfit.)

  • SMPartialOutfit (I dropped in here all partial outfits and bikini versions, sadly due to contamination it actually mostly resembles her standard outfit. You should have an easier time removing parts of it (if you only want her leotard or her torn uniform).

There seems to be some contamination between outfits, I might do a V4 Later. Yup this is actually V3. I had forgotten how much contamination invoking sailor moon in the triggers can cause. So V1 was a mess, V2 lacked separation in the outfits in the dataset and made me unhappy and this is V3, good enough but I get the feeling i might have gotten further separation(or less bleeding) if I made the outfit triggers more unique.

Anyway I'll add the tags summary in the dataset if people want to experiment. This was trained basically on porn doujins so be warned.
